title: Watch: Sleeping otter gets woken up by a poke from a stranger, has best reaction ever
text:
People are the worst. Whatever this sea otter could have been doing before this rude awakening, nothing deserves this.
Today we are all this sea otter, just trying to float along in life without some ass poking us and ruining our sleep. We hope the man responsible for the poking spends the rest of his life on edge waiting for the day when the otter comes to get his revenge.
Via Live Leak
